# PharmIQ Tax Invoice System — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete **Tax Invoice (Bill Receipt) system** for a pharmaceutical distributor desktop application using **CustomTkinter** (UI), **MySQL** (database), and **ReportLab** (PDF generation).

---

