## Key Features Implemented

| Feature | Details |
|---|---|
| **Multi-user branding** | Each distributor gets unique company name, logo, address, GST, DL No displayed |
| **Auto invoice numbering** | `RP00001`, `RP00002`... sequenced per distributor |
| **Customer selection** | Autocomplete search by name/license with auto-fill |
| **Dynamic product rows** | Add/remove rows, popup search, auto-fill batch/MRP/GST |
| **Live calculations** | Real-time subtotal, discount, SGST, CGST, grand total |
| **GST slab summary** | Grouped by 5%, 12%, 18%, 28% slabs in PDF |
| **Amount in words** | Indian numbering (lakhs, crores) |
| **Professional PDF** | A4 layout matching reference image with borders, headers, footer |
| **Stock validation** | Checks available quantity before invoice creation |
| **Bank details & signatory** | Displayed in PDF footer from distributor profile |
| **Print support** | Direct print to default printer |
| **QR/Barcode** | Utility ready for invoice verification codes |

