## How to Run

### 1. Install dependencies
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 2. Configure MySQL
Edit [config.py](file:///f:/Pharmiq/db/config.py) with your MySQL credentials:
```python
DB_CONFIG = {
    "host": "localhost",
    "user": "root",
    "password": "",    # ← your password
    "database": "pharmiq",
}
```

### 3. Launch the app
```bash
python main.py
```
The app will auto-create the database, tables, and seed data on first run.

